| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7121 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 71fb016d-e8d4-5935-b4d8-3a36d6308b9b"
